          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The ratio of the spectrum averaged cross section to",
                " the thermal cross section (effective g-factor) was",
                " obtained by integration of the sum of single-level",
                " Breit-Wigner whose resonance parameters were taken",
                " from the Atlas of Neutron Resonances from 0.2 meV",
                " to 50 eV.",
                "After considering neutron self-sheilding and gamma",
                " attenuation, the effective g-factors are",
                "  0.887+/-0.016 for the 155Gd 88.97 keV gamma line,",
                "  0.859+/-0.016 for the 157Gd 79.51 keV gamma line."
              ]
            }
          ],
