              "free_text": [
                " The uncertainty is propagated from",
                " * uncertainty in the effective g-factor,",
                " * uncertainty in the gamma production cross section:",
                "    - counting statistics",
                "    - gamma detection efficiency",
                "    - normalization by 10B(n,a) cross section.",
